## Validation Method

The evaluation uses:

### LOSO (Leave-One-Subject-Out)

Example:

text Train on: P02 P03 P04 P05 P06 P07 P08  Test on: P01 

Then:

text Train on: P01 P03 P04 P05 P06 P07 P08  Test on: P02 

And so on.

This ensures the model is tested on completely unseen participants.

